69ae01c2ed88e0ffc54783913412a830b1d60b06e512b0f1510f18174a29699d41001c9e94d81caa74ac62a3b1119c68b8188ea1ad928672a3ad056681204d07  dont-rewrite-Os-to-O2.patch
"
